The '''''Thpffftht''''' was a [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] counselor ship in use of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], it took [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] from [[Toola/Legends|Toola]] to the [[Roche system]].

